featured_reviews.review_id: It's a holy place for the Muslims in Dimapur. You will find them going to the masjid everyday to recite their prayers. The place is very airy and right outside the Masjid there are many rice hotels which are owned by the Muslims  where you can get a hearty meal at very reasonable prices and the food is really good. They are very clean in preparing the food especially because they are right outside their holy place and they should not do unclean activities .
